class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\ToolBatchCollectOutcome"
type: readonly final class
summary: "A readonly value object representing the outcome of a tool batch execution within the agent core application. It encapsulates execution status flags, ordered results, and side-effect payloads for downstream processing. Designed to provide a structured, immutable contract for communicating batch processing states."
